name: DEV LIST
tagline: A BADASS list for faster Web Development!
body:
### Hi, my name is Vitor. I am a front-end engineer who lives in Brazil.
Also, I have a **huge passion** for UI/UX and Ruby(rails). Recently, I decided to organize my bookmarks. So, like a good fellow, i'm sharing with you. Hope you enjoy! =]
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
